Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己嘴里说出来有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本人濑川祐太的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可谓是波澜万丈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚懂事的时候就失去了双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然由坚强的姐姐抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在连那姐姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是现在这时候我本应谈着恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并将开始快乐独居生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我的小屋子里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微忍耐一会儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐应该马上就会醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是相当…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是非常糟糕的姿势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一早醒来就被可爱的女孩子抱着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我担心的不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海带  海带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是海带  是肿包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an8}※日语里「こんぶ」是海带 「たんこぶ」是肿包 发音比较相近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于把人家撞飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点大小的包一会儿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问 换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那边换
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  大家换衣服也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就算被看到了也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  你这样对待女孩子  未免也太没礼貌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女生进去过之后一小时内不得入内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来有这么个规定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早饭忘记买了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有早饭么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs24\b1\3c&H18EB66&\pos(156,293)\fad(0,360)}精彩人生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买了好多东西回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之这样就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道你们都喜欢吃什么 所以就各种都买了点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\an8}※发音与「party」相近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内裤啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内裤？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在说聚会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有好多吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以好像想起了生日聚会的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会付自己部分的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么客气的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去打工了  大家慢慢吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门要关关紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁来都不要开门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是迷路了可就不得了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且遇到坏人怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑前我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要听话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走  舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情还没好起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡着的时候抱上去的可是姐姐你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是早饭都没吃就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你想和他一起吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好长~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花了这么多钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么个买法一星期可能都坚持不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他们去旅行前留给我们的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是得把钱付了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是舅舅他也有男子汉的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来得增加打工了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过太晚回家三个人会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把她们抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不容易  但我会多打几份工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大学呢  要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱香小姐  为什么会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  莫非是为了来见我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这种地方碰到祐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱香超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棒读的很彻底嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是莱香小姐想的台词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,织田君  再多融入些感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是佐古学长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说怎么仁村也在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  真巧啊  濑川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然我们是在路上观察研究会共同活动的命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你们是在这埋伏着的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为祐太完全不来路研
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部长说我们这些新入部员要是退部了会很困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入部之后就得好好来参加活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  最近比较忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么气味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻柔甜美  天使般的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一尘不染的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幼女的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们的事情我可没有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是等闲之辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然突然拜托你这种事很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐古学长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我会参加路研的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的话什么时候来都行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濑川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要对你的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,织田君 你突然干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐古学长毫无疑问是危险人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有学长  无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不能让他和我家小孩碰面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间小收拾起来就是轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这房间有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话就是这房间太朴素了  不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有让人心动的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心跳先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心跳先生  在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擦的东西在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比刚开始的时候更乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的衣服也得洗一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有洗衣机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅是怎么洗衣服的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是用手洗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是去洗衣店洗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅说了不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去会遇到坏人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏要是一个人遇到坏人了会害怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟姐姐们一起出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了舅舅  我们必须把衣服洗好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算遇到坏人  三个人一起就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力别害怕一起出门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内衣不能洗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论哪家店都不会洗的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  这上面没有写内衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要洗内裤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感谢舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能住在一起都是多亏了舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个和那个是两码事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可以把内衣一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  专门拿出来洗的话又要花钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200円呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个月都要这么做的话就要6000円
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就加把劲把内衣也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的内衣和舅舅的搅在一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这200円是绝对必要的经费
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100円？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多只要100円？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是家店么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心跳先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,采购食材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  姐姐会做料理么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家庭课的烹饪实习时做过的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有帮过祐理姐做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这些蔬菜买回去料理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能省去不少伙食费呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才200円的损失必须拿回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经阻止不了她了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就开始做晚饭了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷掉的话热一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要先煮饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花是不错  但这花瓶就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生在森林里的瞌睡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏你在画什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  瞌睡先生画好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇  瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说美羽  这个要好好擦掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个可擦不掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是油性笔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正会留下来的  不如画可爱一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡先生  瞌睡先生  瞌睡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当没看见算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炒蔬菜…之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了  非常正确
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  可能会是坏人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏  嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  好像你们很忙  我下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜除水器在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雏也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  把这个放到那边桌子上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快点收拾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小空  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那边没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概几点能回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  今天可能要晚回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅要晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我们先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅不一起吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么也没必要特地去做晚饭了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有早饭剩下的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能一起吃也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了努力打工的舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是早饭剩下的怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是舅舅为了我们买回来的早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以舅舅的晚饭果然还是得我们来做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班表连着果然顶不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是关键哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主食可是牛肉饼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐  冷…静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们懂了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之大家没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭团勉强做成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他好多都失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姑且这是牛肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是炒蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉强去吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,焦的我来吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很棒的晚饭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草莓蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草莓？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这缎带貌似蛮不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  又要了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自家的洗手间已经不能再用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小空  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才谢谢你为我们生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是不是太严厉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么会买蛋糕回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早饭也花了不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心钱的问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然会担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担心不是理所当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们很高兴你为我们买来各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样下去生活费会支持不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是店关门前出售的打折蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有人对我说「慢走」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯独今天我想做些令大家开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没能好好说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始要节约了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起努力的话  总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直没机会和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏  该洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  小雏  一起洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗  大家一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要不一起洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水灵灵的女中学生  空姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在等着她的会是禁断的诱惑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs28\an5\bord3\blur2\fad(500,0)\3c&H149946&\pos(322,240)}少女发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.07,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Happy Girl Happy Happy Girl
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.36,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,いつからかな不思議
